title: Looking To Recruit A Team
body:
Hey all, I'm currently looking for a team that will like to push our rankings to a higher limit and one day be high rated and perhaps known. I am looking mainly for golds and plats. We already have a team name that took only an hour to make. I am looking for all roles and if you are interested feel free to add me via client or skype (csg_cosmic). I will give all information to those who are interested. I look forward to all summoners to join.

{{champion:432}} - CSG Cosmic
